<style>
   @font-face { font-family: 'Edenred';
   src: url('{ basePath }/sfsites/c/resource/res_poc2/fonts/edenred_regular.woff2') format('woff2'); }
   @font-face { font-family: 'Edenred'; font-weight: 700;

   @font-face { font-family: 'Ubuntu';
   src: url('{ basePath }/sfsites/c/resource/res_poc2/fonts/ubuntu_regular.woff2') format('woff2');}

   src: url('{ basePath }/sfsites/c/resource/res_poc2/fonts/ubuntu_bold.woff2') format('woff2');}

     header {
     height: 0px !important;
    }
     body * {
         -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
         box-sizing: border-box;
         text-decoration: none;
        /*font-weight: normal;
        */
         font-style: normal;
    }
     .material-symbols-outlined {
         font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 48 
    }
     .grid {
         display: -ms-grid;
         display: grid;
         -ms-grid-columns: (1fr)[12];
         grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
         -webkit-box-align: stretch;
         -ms-flex-align: stretch;
         align-items: stretch;
    }
     @media screen and (min-width: 501px) and (max-width: 840px) {
         .grid > .betweenFW {
             -ms-grid-column-span: 12 !important;
             grid-column-end: span 12 !important;
        }
    }
     @media screen and (max-width: 500px) {
         .grid > .mobFW {
             -ms-grid-column-span: 12 !important;
             grid-column-end: span 12 !important;
        }
         .grid > .mobMD {
             -ms-grid-column-span: 6 !important;
             grid-column-end: span 6 !important;
        }
    }
    .grid > .colspan8 {
         -ms-grid-column-span: 8;
         grid-column-end: span 8;
    }
    .grid > .colspan4 {
         -ms-grid-column-span: 4;
         grid-column-end: span 4;
    }
    .grid > .colspan2 {
         -ms-grid-column-span: 2;
         grid-column-end: span 2;
    }
    .cardtext {
         padding: 30px 30px 20px 30px;
         text-align: left;
         box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 2px 2px;
         border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
    }
     .cardtext .dt {
         padding: 20px 0;
    }
     .titlelvl3 {
         text-align: left;
         font-family: Edenred;
         font-size: 32px;
         font-weight: 600;
        /*margin: 16px;
        */
    }
     .imgnews img, .imgactivities img {
         border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
         height: 200px;
         width: 100%;
         object-fit: cover;
         object-position: center;
    }
     .titlelvl1 {
         text-align: left;
         font-family: Edenred;
         font-size: 48px;
         margin: 16px;
    }
     .titlelvl4 {
         color: #47576B;
         text-align: left;
         font-family: Edenred;
         font-size: 32px;
         margin: 16px;
    }
     .slds-dropdown__item>a:focus, .slds-dropdown__item>a:hover {
         background-color: transparent;
    }
     .community_layout-section_section-host.comm-section-container {
         padding: 0px;
    }
     .section-content.community_layout-section_section {
         padding: 0px !important;
    }
     .comm-section-container.community_layout-section_section-host {
         padding: 0px !important;
    }
     .section-content.community_layout-section_section {
         padding: 0px !important;
    }
     .slds-map {
         min-width: 100%;
    }
</style>
